hcc_text: Havemeyer Street is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Brooklyn)
info: At Havemeyer Street at South 5th Street and Williamsburg Branch Exit South 5th Street, there were 2 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
